          "settings": {
            "content-title": "What makes a glove match-ready?",
            "content-description": "<p class=\"section-content__text\">One word: grip.</p>\n<p class=\"section-content__text\">Match gloves are built for elite performance. Pro-grade latex. Snug fit. Total confidence on contact. These gloves are made to catch, hold, and dominate — not just survive a session.</p>\n<p class=\"section-content__text\">The latex is softer, the feel is sharper, and the handling is cleaner. They're not built for punishment. They’re built for moments that matter.</p>",
